javax.accessibility.Accessible, GUIConstants, java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, javax.swing.RootPaneContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.swing.WindowConstants
public class NavigationWindow
extends javax.swing.JFrame
implements GUIConstants

The class to display the 3D view for a molecule and navigate into this 3D view.

As it uses Molecule3D to render the molecule, the root atom passed to this class must * NEVER be an hydrogen (see Molecule3D for more details, this class is used quite the same way).

See Also:
Molecule3D, Molecule, Serialized Form
